{"tid":1844300,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍屍page港人講地 罕有地支持 粉嶺抗爭者","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:52:51.000Z","uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe1fec98ad7c1fca725a72c9dbce3f974be5327","tid":1844300,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聲援粉嶺，黃藍合作<br />\n不分政見，共同抗疫</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫手係FB打依句野 洗佢地版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1635006386647434/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F156468627834558%2Fposts%2F1635006386647434%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=6a4ff0ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/156468627834558/posts/1635006386647434/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cjCSPnm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcjCSPnm.jpg&h=51541563&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guLAM82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguLAM82.png&h=7d02d03c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3mkdO3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3mkdO3.png&h=7541d70d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0e9b6b1ad51a49fc6fc0ae7743ae7b1e0158fd4","tid":1844300,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:40:57.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"738c84827ea6f68a1eb42ee9ef9a4d2b728b3c4a","tid":1844300,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"仲有好多藍絲鬧佢地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1617d191501a010ba9a8cf37c1efef31bc585e2","tid":1844300,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T00:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1a93a7eaaa26ae349e21a9b16dab14d139d637","tid":1844300,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T01:05:38.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見，抗疫是良知！"},{"pid":"176656b9c2d3582a6ad355bd45745083b1c984ca","tid":1844300,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"仲有啲住大陸五毛唔知頭唔知路，就盲反話邊有居民燒自己間屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連燒緊咩邨都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}